trans-unit.source: Represents user login information for forms authentication by using client application services.
trans-unit.target: Representerer brukerinformasjon pålogging for skjemagodkjenning ved hjelp av klienten programtjenester.

trans-unit.source: The ClientFormsAuthenticationCredentials class is used by the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.IClientFormsAuthenticationCredentialsProvider> interface.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ClientFormsAuthenticationCredentials brukes av den <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.IClientFormsAuthenticationCredentialsProvider>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.IClientFormsAuthenticationCredentialsProvider>

trans-unit.source: When you implement this interface, you must return a populated instance of this class in your <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.IClientFormsAuthenticationCredentialsProvider.GetCredentials%2A> implementation.
trans-unit.target: Når du implementerer dette grensesnittet, må du gå tilbake en fylt forekomst av denne klassen i din <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.IClientFormsAuthenticationCredentialsProvider.GetCredentials%2A>implementering.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.IClientFormsAuthenticationCredentialsProvider.GetCredentials%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientFormsAuthenticationCredentials"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientFormsAuthenticationCredentials"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: You will typically pass user-provided values as the parameters of this constructor.

trans-unit.target: Brukernavnet.

trans-unit.source: A value indicating whether the user credentials should be saved and reused for subsequent login attempts.
trans-unit.target: En verdi som angir om brukerlegitimasjonen skal lagret og brukt på nytt for etterfølgende påloggingsforsøk.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the user password.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir brukerpassord.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientFormsAuthenticationMembershipProvider> class uses this property to retrieve the user password during authentication.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientFormsAuthenticationMembershipProvider>klassen bruker denne egenskapen til å hente brukerpassord under godkjenning.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientFormsAuthenticationMembershipProvider>
